des: Wilkins Harley-Davidson Voice Briefing covers a great deal of new exciting motorcycle topics as well as some history with a focus on Harley-Davidson. Including topics such as the new Electric Motorcycle, LiveWire, the History of Harley-Davidson, current issues relating to motorcycling and more. You are bound to learn something new in this 1 to 2 minute voice briefing.
